parameters: \nw[Town Mayor]Phew, I can't keep up with how busy I am.

\nw[Town Mayor]If it's a message to another town or a request
from Prae, there's no helping it.

\nw[Prae]I have business with this person, so I'll ask you
two to explain.
'メイド'
\nw[Louis]Oh, Taro-sama. What seems to be the matter?
Let's talk
No need
話をする
\nw[Taro]Huh, wasn't she at the reception?

\nw[Louis]Yes, until just now. But I'm not constantly
watching, you know?

\nw[Taro]Ah, that's right... But more importantly, has
anything changed about the way you speak?

\nw[Louis]Are you saying that I've changed since the
reception? I am a maid, so it's only natural,
isn't it?
\nw[Taro]It's troublesome to be told as if it's natural...

\nw[Taro](I feel like your voice and physique have changed
somehow...)
\nw[Taro]Come to think of it, haven't you been called Rumi?
\nw[Louis]I won't talk about the Water Temple, you know?
\nw[Taro]It's fine, just the way you address me.
'メイド'

\nw[Louis]Yes, that's right. However, I can see that there
is something else you want to ask. Shall we get to
the main point?

\nw[Taro]......You seem to see through a lot of
things......Well, I guess it's good that you get
to the point quickly......

\nw[Taro]I want to have Prae examined by a witch. Is there
any way to do that?
\nw[Louis]Please rely on someone other than me.
\nw[Taro]So, that means it's not possible?
\nw[Louis]I don't have any connections, so...

\nw[Taro]I see... You have a wide network, so I thought
maybe you could help...

\nw[Louis]How about hiring an information broker yourself?
It would be beneficial for the future to have
reliable connections other than me.
\nw[Taro]Yeah... I understand. Thank you.
A
用はない
\nw[Louis]Is that so?
\nw[Taro]By the way, is that person Fee a student?
'メイド'

\nw[Louis]That outfit is one of my cosplay costumes. Since
Fee often breaks clothes, I often give her clothes
as presents.
